   3.) Requirements
  ==================
  
   Stat466 requires the following software to run:
   
    - Python Programming Language: <www.python.org>
    - PyQt4: <http://www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk/software/pyqt/download>
   
   
   4.) Installation and  Run
  ===========================
   
   To run Stat466 start the file stat466.py with python.
   
   You can also use python setuptools to install Stat466.
   
